---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PineTree from '../components/PineTree.astro';
import Leaf from '../components/Leaf.astro';

const stats = [
  { label: "Annual Sales", value: "$246M" },
  { label: "Active Stores", value: "179" },
  { label: "Price/Gram", value: "$6.62" }
];
---

<Layout title="Cannabis Entrepreneur Resource" description="44 expert guides for Maine cannabis entrepreneurs. Licensing, compliance, real estate, taxation, and operations — everything you need to open and scale." heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511497584788-876760111969?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400">
  <section class="premium-hero">
    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-content reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <div class="hero-badge">Updated for 2026</div>
        <h1>The Professional Gateway to Maine's Cannabis Market</h1>
        <p>Expert-vetted guides for navigating licensing, compliance, and growth in the Pine Tree State.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/" class="btn-main">Start Your Application</a>
          <a href="/roi-calculator/" class="btn-secondary">Calculate Your ROI</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="floating-icons">
            <PineTree size={120} color="var(--color-background)" class="logo-pine" />
            <Leaf size={80} color="var(--color-soft-green)" class="logo-leaf" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="market-bar">
    <div class="bar-container">
      {stats.map(stat => (
        <div class="bar-item">
          <span class="bar-label">{stat.label}:</span>
          <span class="bar-value">{stat.value}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
      <a href="/market-stats/" class="bar-link">Full Report &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="newsletter-strip">
    <div class="newsletter-content">
      <div class="newsletter-text">
        <h3>Stay Current with Maine Cannabis</h3>
        <p>Get notified when we update guides or add new resources. No spam, just signal.</p>
      </div>
      <form class="newsletter-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xvgzlowz" method="POST">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required aria-label="Email address" class="newsletter-input" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Newsletter Signup - Maine Dispensary Guide" />
        <button type="submit" class="newsletter-btn">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="mission-statement">
    <div class="mission-content">
      <h2>Build Your Passion Project</h2>
      <p>Opening a dispensary in Maine is a real business with real regulations. But if you've got a vision for what your shop could be — this guide exists to help you get there without getting tripped up on compliance.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="market-overview reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
    <div class="overview-content">
      <h2>Why Choose the Maine Cannabis Market?</h2>
      <p>Maine has a medical program that's been around since 1999 and an adult-use market that's been growing since 2020. That means established patterns, more data, and a clearer picture of what works than newer markets. The state is overseen by the <a href="/glossary/" title="View Technical Glossary">Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</a>, and towns have to opt-in before you can open a store — which means do your homework on location before you sign anything.</p>
      <p>Whether you're an experienced operator or starting from scratch, Maine rewards preparation. You need to know local ordinances, how to find compliant real estate, and how to handle IRS 280E. Our <a href="/guides/" title="Explore all dispensary guides">municipal guides</a> and <a href="/about/" title="Read about our methodology">resources</a> cover the specifics you need to actually open your doors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="overview-decoration" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="deco-ring"></div>
      <div class="deco-ring"></div>
      <div class="deco-ring"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="operational-excellence reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
    <div class="excellence-content">
      <h2>What It Takes to Run One</h2>
      <p>Getting a license is just the start. Running a dispensary well means managing inventory, staying compliant with security rules, and actually knowing what you're selling. Maine customers — especially in Portland and surrounding areas — care about craft and transparency. That means the shops that do the work on staff training tend to build real loyalty.</p>
      <p>We cover the operational stuff: <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-pos/">POS systems</a>, <a href="/glossary/#metrc">Metrc tracking</a>, security requirements. Our <a href="/launch-checklist/">Launch Checklist</a> walks through what you need before opening day. Compliance isn't optional here — it's how you stay open.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="excellence-decoration" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="deco-leaf" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M50 5 C30 25 10 50 50 95 C90 50 70 25 50 5" opacity="0.1"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="core-hubs reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Core Topics</h2>
      <p>Pick a category to dig into.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hub-grid">
      <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/" class="hub-card">
        <div class="hub-icon">📜</div>
        <h3>Licensing</h3>
        <p>Step-by-step state and local approval maps.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-taxation-280e/" class="hub-card">
        <div class="hub-icon">⚖️</div>
        <h3>Compliance</h3>
        <p>Mastering 280E and OCP tracking rules.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/" class="hub-card">
        <div class="hub-icon">📍</div>
        <h3>Real Estate</h3>
        <p>Finding compliant zones in every town.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/roi-calculator/" class="hub-card">
        <div class="hub-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>ROI Calculator</h3>
        <p>Estimate startup costs and break-even timelines.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/resources/" class="hub-card">
        <div class="hub-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Vendors</h3>
        <p>Connect with expert lawyers and CPAs.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="geo-explorer reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
    <div class="explorer-content">
      <h2>Explore Municipal Guides</h2>
      <p>Local zoning and competitive analysis for Maine's "Opt-In" communities.</p>
      <div class="city-chips">
        <a href="/guides/portland-dispensary-guide/">Portland</a>
        <a href="/guides/augusta-dispensary-guide/">Augusta</a>
        <a href="/guides/bangor-dispensary-guide/">Bangor</a>
        <a href="/guides/lewiston-dispensary-guide/">Lewiston</a>
        <a href="/guides/south-portland-dispensary-guide/">South Portland</a>
        <a href="/guides/biddeford-dispensary-guide/">Biddeford</a>
        <a href="/guides/auburn-dispensary-guide/">Auburn</a>
      </div>
      <a href="/guides/" class="btn-secondary">View All 41 Guides &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="whats-new reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
    <div class="whats-new-header">
      <div class="freshness-indicator">
        <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
        <span class="freshness-text">Updated April 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h2>What's New</h2>
      <p>Recent updates and additions to the guide library.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="new-guides-grid">
      <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-costs/" class="new-guide-card">
        <span class="new-badge">Updated</span>
        <span class="new-guide-title">2026 Startup Costs Breakdown</span>
        <span class="new-guide-date">April 4, 2026</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/guides/bangor-dispensary-guide/" class="new-guide-card">
        <span class="new-badge">Updated</span>
        <span class="new-guide-title">Bangor Market Analysis</span>
        <span class="new-guide-date">April 3, 2026</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/" class="new-guide-card">
        <span class="new-badge">Updated</span>
        <span class="new-guide-title">Real Estate & Zoning Guide</span>
        <span class="new-guide-date">April 2, 2026</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/launch-checklist/" class="new-guide-card">
        <span class="new-badge new">New</span>
        <span class="new-guide-title">2026 Launch Checklist</span>
        <span class="new-guide-date">April 1, 2026</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="social-proof reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.7s;">
    <div class="proof-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">2,847</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Entrepreneurs Served</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">44</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Expert Guides</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">15</span>
        <span class="stat-label">City Guides</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-value">98%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Update Accuracy</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="start-here reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
    <div class="start-here-content">
      <h2>New to Maine Cannabis?</h2>
      <p>Start your journey here. This curated path walks you through the essentials.</p>
      <div class="journey-steps">
        <a href="/launch-checklist/" class="journey-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <h3>Get the Launch Checklist</h3>
            <p>The complete roadmap from concept to opening day.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/" class="journey-step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <h3>Understand Licensing</h3>
            <p>OCP requirements, municipal opt-in, and application timeline.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/roi-calculator/" class="journey-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <h3>Run the Numbers</h3>
            <p>Model your startup costs against Maine's $246M market.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/" class="journey-step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <h3>Find Your Location</h3>
            <p>Zoning rules, commercial leases, and municipal requirements.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .premium-hero {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-background);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-radius: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 100%;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .premium-hero {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-background);
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    color: var(--color-background);
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    color: var(--color-background);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-main {
    background: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-background);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 350px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .visual-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: 3.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(2deg); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
  }

  .logo-pine { animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .logo-leaf { animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite reverse; margin-left: -30px; margin-top: 50px; }

  .market-bar {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bar-container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .bar-item { font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  .bar-label { color: var(--color-text-light); font-weight: 600; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
  .bar-value { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 700; }
  .bar-link { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; }

  /* Newsletter Strip */
  .newsletter-strip {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .newsletter-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-text h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .newsletter-text p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .newsletter-input {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    min-width: 220px;
    background: white;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .newsletter-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(13, 78, 80, 0.1);
  }

  .newsletter-btn {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
  }

  .newsletter-btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  .newsletter-btn:active {
    transform: scale(0.97);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .newsletter-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .newsletter-form {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .newsletter-input { min-width: unset; width: 100%; }
    .newsletter-btn { width: 100%; }
  }

  .mission-statement { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 6rem; }
  .mission-content h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .mission-content p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .market-overview { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 6rem; background: var(--color-surface); padding: 4rem 2rem; border-radius: 2.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .market-overview::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent), var(--color-primary)); }
  .overview-content h2 { font-size: 2.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .overview-content p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .overview-content a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .overview-content a:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); }

  .overview-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    right: -50px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .deco-ring {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.06;
  }

  .deco-ring:nth-child(2) { width: 60px; height: 60px; margin-left: 20px; }
  .deco-ring:nth-child(3) { width: 40px; height: 40px; margin-left: 40px; }

  @media (max-width: 850px) {
    .overview-decoration { display: none; }
  }

  .operational-excellence { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8rem; padding: 0 2rem; position: relative; }
  .excellence-content h2 { font-size: 2.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .excellence-content p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .excellence-content a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .excellence-content a:hover { border-color: var(--color-accent); }

  .excellence-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    left: -30px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 150px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .deco-leaf {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 850px) {
    .excellence-decoration { display: none; }
  }

  .core-hubs { margin-bottom: 8rem; }
  .hub-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .hub-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.2, 1);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hub-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-12px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(13, 78, 80, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .hub-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
  }

  .hub-card:hover .hub-icon { transform: scale(1.2) rotate(8deg); }
  .hub-card h3 { margin: 0 0 0.75rem; color: var(--color-primary); font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .hub-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.6; }

  .geo-explorer { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8rem; }
  .city-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 3.5rem;
  }

  .city-chips a {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .city-chips a:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 850px) {
    .hero-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .hero-btns { justify-content: center; }
    .hero-visual { display: none; }
    .bar-container { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
  }

  /* What's New Section */
  .whats-new {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .whats-new-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .freshness-indicator {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.1);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pulse-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
  }

  .freshness-text {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .whats-new h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .whats-new > .whats-new-header > p { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .new-guides-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .new-guide-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

